  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 106.4,
    "text": "But it looks to me like you fellows have got a lot of bags there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.4,
    "endTime": 113.5,
    "text": "You two lady killers are too smart to be without one of my patented candy bar bag carrying bags."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.5,
