  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.7,
    "endTime": 130.0,
    "text": "Well, maybe if they didn't stretch the truth, they wouldn't sell as many."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "That's it, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.0,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "We've got to stretch the truth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 137.8,
    "text": "Chocolate!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.8,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "Yes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "Hello, young lady."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 144.6,
    "text": "We're selling chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.6,
    "endTime": 147.5,
    "text": "Is your mother home?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.5,
    "endTime": 149.2,
    "text": "Mom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.2,
    "endTime": 150.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.0,
    "endTime": 151.9,
    "text": "What's all the yelling?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.9,
    "endTime": 156.3,
    "text": "You just can't wait for me to die, can you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.3,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "They're selling chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.0,
    "endTime": 159.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.0,
    "endTime": 161.0,
    "text": "They're selling chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 162.5,
    "text": "They're selling chocolate?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.5,
    "endTime": 163.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.0,
    "endTime": 164.0,
    "text": "Chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.0,
    "endTime": 167.7,
    "text": "I remember when they first invented chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.7,
    "endTime": 169.0,
    "text": "I always hated it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 171.8,
    "text": "Oh, but this chocolate's not for eating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.8,
    "endTime": 175.8,
    "text": "You rub it on your skin and it makes you live forever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.8,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "No, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 179.2,
    "text": "Live forever, you say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.2,
    "endTime": 182.0,
    "text": "I'll take one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.0,
    "endTime": 184.2,
    "text": "Come on, you lazy Mary."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.2,
    "endTime": 187.1,
    "text": "Start rubbing me with that chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "I hate you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 194.0,
    "text": "If we keep exaggerating the truth, we'll be fancy living in no time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.0,
    "endTime": 197.4,
    "text": "Hooray for lying!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.4,
    "endTime": 202.1,
    "text": "This guy'll feel so sorry for us, he'll have to buy all of our chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.1,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "What can I do for you boys?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 205.4,
    "text": "Hello, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.4,
    "endTime": 206.70000000000002,
    "text": "Would you like to buy a chocolate bar?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.7,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "We need an operation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "Really? Small world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 213.5,
    "text": "What's the matter with you guys?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.5,
    "endTime": 217.5,
    "text": "We've got some head trauma and eternal bleeding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.5,
    "endTime": 219.0,
    "text": "Some guys have all the luck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.0,
    "endTime": 222.0,
    "text": "I was born with glass bones and paper skin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.0,
    "endTime": 226.3,
    "text": "Every morning I break my legs, and every afternoon I break my arms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.3,
    "endTime": 230.60000000000002,
    "text": "At night, I lie awake in agony until my heart attacks put me to sleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.6,
    "endTime": 233.2,
    "text": "Oh, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.2,
    "endTime": 235.0,
    "text": "Quick, Patrick, let's help him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.0,
    "endTime": 235.7,
    "text": "Careful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.7,
    "endTime": 239.0,
    "text": "Put him down gently."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.0,
    "endTime": 239.7,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.7,
    "endTime": 241.6,
    "text": "Poor, poor man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.6,
    "endTime": 244.4,
    "text": "If there's anything we can do to help you..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.4,
    "endTime": 246.20000000000002,
    "text": "There is one thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.2,
    "endTime": 250.2,
    "text": "As you can well imagine, my medical bills are extremely high."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.2,
    "endTime": 259.8,
    "text": "But luckily I'm able to keep myself alive by selling chocolate bars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.8,
    "endTime": 261.40000000000003,
    "text": "Such nice boys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.4,
    "endTime": 273.79999999999995,
    "text": "It does my heart good to con a couple of classy suckeroonies like those two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.8,
    "endTime": 277.0,
    "text": "Let's face it, Patrick, we're failures."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.0,
    "endTime": 281.5,
    "text": "I can live with that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.5,
    "endTime": 283.7,
    "text": "Chocolate!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.7,
    "endTime": 287.4,
    "text": "I've been trying to catch you boys all day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.4,
    "endTime": 289.5,
    "text": "I'd like to buy all your chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.5,
    "endTime": 291.0,
    "text": "Good evening, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.0,
    "endTime": 292.5,
    "text": "Table for one, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.5,
    "endTime": 296.5,
    "text": "Sorry, but the whole restaurant has been rented to a private party."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.5,
    "endTime": 299.2,
    "text": "Who could afford to rent out the whole restaurant?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.0,
    "endTime": 303.0,
